    {
      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "$49,000 - This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior paint and body panels are flawless, with no scratches, dents, or imperfections. The interior is in pristine condition, showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or carpets. All mechanical systems and electronic components are in perfect working order.",
